%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nancy%20Pelosi%20praises%20the%20'exquisite'%20indictments%20against%20Trump%3A%20'They're%20beautiful%20and%20intricate'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Former%20House%20Speaker%20Nancy%20Pelosi%20after%20throwing%20out%20the%20ceremonial%20first%20pitch%20at%20Nationals%20Park%20on%20June%206%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d0f623f5d4870019e2f38b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20House%20Speaker%20Nancy%20Pelosi%20after%20throwing%20out%20the%20ceremonial%20first%20pitch%20at%20Nationals%20Park%20on%20June%206%2C%202023.%3Cp%3ERob%20Carr%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPelosi%20praised%20the%20two%20federal%20Trump%20indictments%20as%20%26quot%3Bexquisite%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bintricate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThey%20probably%20have%20a%20better%20chance%20of%20conviction%20than%20anything%20that%20I%20would%20come%20up%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20former%20speaker%20arguably%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20indictment%20by%20creating%20the%20January%206%20committee.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20House%20Speaker%20Nancy%20Pelosi%20is%20offering%20high%20praise%20for%20the%20two%20federal%20indictments%20against%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20indictments%20against%20the%20president%20are%20exquisite%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnymag.com%2Fintelligencer%2F2023%2F08%2Fhow-nancy-pelosi-long-game-led-to-trumps-indictment.html%5C%22%3Ean%20interview%20with%20New%20York%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20beautiful%20and%20intricate%2C%20and%20they%20probably%20have%20a%20better%20chance%20of%20conviction%20than%20anything%20that%20I%20would%20come%20up%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnymag.com%2Fintelligencer%2F2023%2F08%2Fhow-nancy-pelosi-long-game-led-to-trumps-indictment.html%5C%22%3Ethat%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Pelosi%20reflected%20more%20broadly%20on%20the%20role%20that%20the%20January%206%20committee%20%E2%80%94%20a%20select%20committee%20that%20Pelosi%20created%20after%20Senate%20Republicans%20blocked%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20bipartisan%209%2F11-style%20commission%20%E2%80%94%20played%20in%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20Trump's%20indictment%20over%20his%20efforts%20to%20overturn%20the%202020%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20on%20January%206%20that%20he%20had%20committed%20a%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pelosi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Trump's%20first%20federal%20indictment%20%E2%80%94%20which%20includes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-indictment-read-charges-mar-a-lago-records-case-2023-6%5C%22%3E37%20charges%20in%20relation%20to%20his%20handling%20of%20classified%20documents%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20had%20little%20to%20do%20with%20the%20work%20of%20the%20committee%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-indictment-read-charges-january-6-election-case-2023-7%5C%22%3Esecond%20indictment%20brought%20by%20Special%20Counsel%20Jack%20Smith%20last%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20arguably%20would%20not%20have%20happened%20without%20the%20work%20of%20the%20January%206%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20want%20them%20to%20pay%20attention%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20that%20we%20got%20their%20attention%2C%26quot%3B%20Pelosi%20said%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20the%20presentation%20%E2%80%94%20the%20narrative%20%E2%80%94%20had%20to%20be%20the%20way%20it%20was.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20committee%20laid%20out%20a%20narrative%20making%20the%20case%20that%20Trump%20engaged%20in%20criminal%20behavior%2C%20the%20DOJ%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Finvestigations%2F2023%2F06%2F19%2Ffbi-resisted-opening-probe-into-trumps-role-jan-6-more-than-year%2F%5C%22%3Ewas%20not%20yet%20undertaking%20efforts%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20investigate%20the%20former%20president.%20Nonetheless%2C%20the%20narrative%20laid%20out%20in%20last%20week's%2045-page%20indictment%20bore%20a%20strong%20resemblance%20to%20the%20narrative%20laid%20out%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govinfo.gov%2Fcontent%2Fpkg%2FGPO-J6-REPORT%2Fpdf%2FGPO-J6-REPORT.pdf%5C%22%3Ereport%20that%20the%20committee%20released%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20last%20Congress.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPelosi%20noted%20that%20she%20made%20her%20appointments%20to%20the%20committee%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20building%20that%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20were%20accepting%20the%20offer%20to%20be%20on%20the%20committee%2C%20they%20knew%20that%20it%20wasn't%20going%20to%20be%20every%20five%20minutes%20that%20they'd%20be%20speaking%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pelosi.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20part%20of%20the%20plan%20%5Bto%20present%5D%20a%20narrative%20for%20the%20public%20to%20understand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnancy-pelosi-trump-indictments-exquisite-beautiful-intricate-january-6-classified-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691419174000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d0f630f5d4870019e2f39c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnancy-pelosi-trump-indictments-exquisite-beautiful-intricate-january-6-classified-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThey%20probably%20have%20a%20better%20chance%20of%20conviction%20than%20anything%20that%20I%20would%20come%20up%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Pelosi%20said%20of%20the%20two%20federal%20indictments%20against%20Trump.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bmetzger%40insider.com%20(Bryan%20Metzger)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnancy-pelosi-trump-indictments-exquisite-beautiful-intricate-january-6-classified-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20As%20Violence%20Rages%20On%2C%20MLAs%20Divided%20Over%20Whether%20or%20Not%20to%20Hold%20Special%20Assembly%20Session%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Even%20as%20Manipur%20continues%20to%20burn%20requiring%20the%20Centre%20to%20dispatch%20additional%20forces%20to%20the%20strife-torn%20state%2C%20tension%20is%20building%20up%20around%20holding%20a%20special%20session%20of%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20to%20discuss%20the%20ongoing%20turmoil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20has%20now%20reached%20the%20door%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20(PMO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAthouba%20Khuraijam%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Coordinating%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Integrity%20(COCOMI)%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20and%20some%20other%20representatives%20of%20the%20Committee%20went%20to%20the%20PMO%20to%20physically%20submit%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fmanipur%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-violence-cocomi-demands-special-manipur-legislative-assembly-session-before-august-5-623592-2023-07-29%5C%22%3Eresolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20taken%20at%20a%20public%20meeting%20on%20July%2029%20in%20Imphal%20calling%20for%20such%20a%20session.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20asked%20to%20spell%20out%20why%20such%20a%20session%20is%20particularly%20needed%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20Athouba%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20demand%20has%20been%20raised%20from%20our%20side%20because%20we%20have%20not%20seen%20any%20initiative%20from%20the%20legislators%20or%20the%20state%20government%20to%20discuss%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House.%20The%20assembly%20is%20not%20dissolved%2C%20so%20it%20must%20assemble%20to%20deliberate%20on%20what%20is%20going%20on%20in%20the%20state%2C%20including%20discussing%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20from%20a%20set%20of%20MLAs.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%2010%20MLAs%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community%20have%20stated%20their%20individual%20positions%20on%20the%20matter%20which%20should%20be%20stated%20also%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House.%20There%20are%20outside%20forces%20acting%20in%20the%20state%3B%20people%20are%20asking%2C%20where%20is%20the%20assembly%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20also%20noticed%20some%20sitting%20MLAs%20engaging%20in%20things%20which%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%2C%20being%20a%20member%20of%20the%20assembly.%20Such%20things%20must%20be%20put%20on%20record.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20July%2029%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fmanipur%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-violence-cocomi-demands-special-manipur-legislative-assembly-session-before-august-5-623592-2023-07-29%5C%22%3Eresolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20taken%20as%20part%20of%20a%20mass%20rally%20held%20in%20the%20Imphal%20valley.%20As%20per%20news%20reports%2C%20around%20two%20lakh%20people%20took%20part%20in%20that%20rally%20where%20some%20speakers%20also%20criticized%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20and%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20state%20chief%20minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20to%20quell%20the%20violence%20in%20the%20border%20state.%20In%20that%20session%2C%20those%20assembled%20urged%20the%20Governor%2C%20the%20speaker%20and%20the%20state%20government%20to%20hold%20that%20special%20session%20by%20August%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20it%2C%20several%20other%20valley-based%20civil%20society%20organisations%20had%20also%20taken%20a%20similar%20resolution.%20On%20July%2027%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20information%20and%20public%20relations%20minister%20Sapam%20Ranjan%20told%20the%20local%20press%20that%20the%20Cabinet%20had%20approved%20a%20special%20session%20and%20the%20request%20had%20been%20forwarded%20to%20the%20governor.%20Ranjan%20said%20the%20Cabinet%20has%20asked%20for%20a%20special%20session%20in%20the%20third%20week%20of%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20hold%20the%20session%20by%20the%20August%205%20deadline%20of%20the%20COCOMI%2C%20it%20has%20now%20called%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20boycott%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20reaching%20out%20to%20Paolienlal%20Haokip%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20the%2010%20Kuki%20MLAs%20demanding%20a%20separate%20administration%20for%20the%20Kuki%20residents%20of%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20if%20he%20would%20attend%20such%20a%20session%20if%20the%20governor%20accepts%20the%20Cabinet%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20categorically%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWho%20would%20give%20assurance%20of%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20Kuki%20MLAs%20going%20to%20Imphal%20to%20attend%20the%20assembly%20session%3F%20At%20this%20point%2C%20I%20would%20say%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20and%20also%20not%20necessary%20to%20participate%20in%20it%20as%20the%20separation%20of%20the%20state%20is%20complete.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07195859%2Fmanipur_assembly_session_2_20150625_1176793276.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07195859%2Fmanipur_assembly_session_2_20150625_1176793276.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07195859%2Fmanipur_assembly_session_2_20150625_1176793276-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667037%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManipur%20Assembly.%20Photo%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.assembly.mn.gov.in%2F%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20asked%20whether%20he%20is%20still%20hopeful%20of%20his%20party%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20relenting%20to%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20to%20the%20Kukis%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20hope%2C%20we%20hope%2C%20it%20would.%20Also%2C%20BJP%20is%20a%20national%20party%3B%20it%20is%20not%20about%20fulfilling%20the%20political%20ambitions%20of%20someone%20by%20causing%20communal%20violence.%20I%20hope%20it%20takes%20action%20against%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20another%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%2C%20L.M.%20Khaute%2C%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fmanipur-kuki-mlas-likely-to-skip-assembly-session-over-safety-concerns-fresh-violence-prompts-additional-deployment-latest-updates-news-308589%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20PTI%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20view%20of%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20possible%20on%20my%20part%20to%20attend%20the%20upcoming%20session.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilson%20Lalam%20Hangshing%2C%20co-founder%20of%20the%20regional%20party%2C%20Kuki%20People%E2%80%99s%20Alliance%20(KPA)%2C%20which%20has%20two%20MLAs%2C%20too%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20his%20party%20colleagues%20would%20not%20attend%20the%20session.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20session%20has%20been%20arranged%20by%20the%20state%20cabinet%20at%20the%20call%20of%20a%20fascist%20organisation%20like%20COCOMI%20which%20has%20no%20locus%20standi%20on%20the%20matter.%20Manipur%20is%20now%20being%20ruled%20by%20a%20mob%3B%20there%20is%20no%20government%20there%3B%20the%20government%20has%20surrendered%20to%20