0decision%20to%20relocate%20the%20CHS%E2%80%99%20library%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fromila-thapar%5C%22%3Ehistorian%20Romila%20Thapar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pointed%20to%20the%20extensive%20and%20diverse%20set%20of%20resources%20currently%20housed%20at%20the%20CHS%E2%80%99%20library%2C%20and%20how%20it%20has%20benefitted%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20post-graduate%20and%20research%20scholars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20CHS%20faculty%20brought%20resources%20from%20archives%20and%20libraries%20across%20India%20and%20the%20world%20(from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20%5Bthe%5D%20French%20Archives)%20to%20the%20library%20to%20facilitate%20teaching%20and%20research%2C%E2%80%9D%20their%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20rich%20collection%20of%20primary%20sources%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20volumes%20of%20inscriptions%2C%20literary%20texts%2C%20and%20archival%20documents%2C%20as%20well%20as%20important%20secondary%20sources%20of%20a%20high%20academic%20standing%20were%20housed%20in%20the%20library%20%E2%80%A6%20The%20library%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20of%20immense%20value%20for%20students%20at%20the%20post-graduate%20and%20research%20levels.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20following%20the%20CHS%20example%2C%20other%20centres%20have%20also%20set%20up%20departmental%20libraries%20in%20the%20university.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20wrote%20about%20how%20the%20CHS%20received%20grants%20from%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20specifically%20to%20build%20the%20library%20and%20later%20to%20double%20its%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiven%20this%20history%20of%20the%20CHS%20library%2C%20as%20faculty%20who%20have%20nurtured%20this%20institution%20over%20past%20several%20decades%2C%20we%20feel%20that%20the%20library%E2%80%99s%20relocation%20and%20dispersal%20would%20essentially%20destroy%20this%20fine%20institution%20which%20was%20funded%20specifically%20for%20the%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20their%20letter%20concluded%20by%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20historians%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20JNU%20administration%20seems%20to%20have%20decided%20to%20move%20the%20CHS%20library%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20even%20consulting%20the%20CHS%20faculty%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20full%20copy%20of%20their%20letter%20has%20been%20reproduced%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJNU%20students%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20library%E2%80%99s%20future%20last%20week%20when%20speculation%20arose%20that%20the%20administration%20was%20going%20to%20shut%20it%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMaktoob%20Media%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmaktoobmedia.com%2Flatest-news%2Fjnu-to-shut-down-centre-for-historical-studies-library-students-say-not-an-isolated-move%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20signboards%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98Special%20Centre%20for%20Tamil%20Studies%E2%80%99%20were%20also%20installed%20in%20front%20of%20the%20CHS%20library%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EJNU%20implements%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FNEP2020%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23NEP2020%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20vision%20and%20mission%20of%20PM%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20by%20beginning%20the%20Special%20Centre%20for%20Tamil%20Studies%20which%20introduces%20special%20courses%2C%20translation%20and%20learning%20of%20the%20oldest%20language%20and%20its%20great%20culture.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frashtrapatibhvn%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40rashtrapatibhvn%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FB5VHHSqGdK%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FB5VHHSqGdK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%20(%40JNU_official_50)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJNU_official_50%2Fstatus%2F1686078141826240512%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2031%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20administration%20clarified%20on%20Friday%20(August%204)%20that%20it%20was%20not%20shutting%20the%20CHS%20library%20down%20and%20said%20that%20claims%20saying%20otherwise%20were%20%E2%80%9Cmisinformation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20members%2Fstudents%20concerned%20of%20the%20university%20are%20hereby%20informed%20that%20as%20part%20of%20an%20internal%20arrangement%2C%20the%20university%20has%20planned%20to%20relocate%20the%20existing%20CHS%20Library%20to%20the%20adjoining%20building%2C%E2%80%9D%20its%20statement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fjnu-junks-claims-of-library-closure-says-its-being-relocated%2F1701392%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fjnu-shut-down-history-centre-library-allege-students-8875955%2F%5C%22%3Econtinued%20to%20say%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20executive%20committee%20met%20on%20May%2030%20to%20%E2%80%9Capprove%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%20Space%20Committee%20regarding%20%5Bthe%5D%20Special%20Centre%20for%20Tamil%20Studies%2C%20allocating%20them%20the%20building%2Fpremises%20adjacent%20to%20EXIM%20Bank%20Library%2C%20i.e.%20%5Bthe%5D%20CHS%20Library%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Studies%20centre%20will%20move%20into%20the%20CHS%20library%20building%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20will%20move%20to%20the%20EXIM%20Bank%20Library.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20students%20say%20that%20the%20latter%20will%20be%20unable%20to%20accommodate%20everything%20from%20the%20CHS%20library.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20as%20students%20who%20are%20important%20stakeholders%20of%20the%20university%2C%20were%20not%20consulted%E2%80%A6%20There%20is%20very%20limited%20space%20in%20the%20EXIM%20Bank%20Library.%20Only%20a%20few%20books%20can%20be%20shifted.%20We%20do%20not%20know%20what%20is%20going%20to%20happen%20to%20the%20remaining%20books%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20anonymous%20PhD%20scholar%20told%20%3Cem%3EIE.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EProf.%20Santishree%20Dhulipudi%20Pandit%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EVice%20Chancellor%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EJawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%2008.%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubject%3A%20Reports%20pertaining%20to%20the%20relocation%20of%20the%20CHS%20CAS%20Library%20and%20reallocation%20of%20the%20Library%20Building%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadam%20Vice%20Chancellor%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%2C%20the%20former%20faculty%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Historical%20Studies%2C%20are%20shocked%20to%20hear%20that%20the%20CHS%20library%20building%20is%20being%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20administration%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20the%20need%20for%20space%20for%20new%20centres%20that%20are%20being%20established%20within%20the%20university.%20Since%20the%20grant%20for%20the%20building%20of%20the%20CHS%20library%20was%20received%20expressly%20for%20this%20purpose%20from%20the%20UGC%2C%20it%20is%20quite%20disturbing%20to%20hear%20that%20the%20building%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20put%20to%20alternate%20use%20after%20several%20decades%20of%20its%20existence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CHS%20received%20a%20Department%20of%20Special%20Assistance%20(DSA)%20status%20from%20the%20UGC%20in%20the%20late%201980s%20that%20was%20aimed%20at%20developing%20the%20research%20and%20teaching%20in%20the%20Centre.%20The%20faculty%20requested%20that%20the%20grant%20promised%20be%20allowed%20to%20be%20used%20not%20for%20more%20faculty%20positions%2C%20as%20was%20the%20current%20practice%2C%20but%20to%20build%20an%20exclusive%20departmental%20library%20of%20the%20CHS%2C%20necessary%20for%20teaching%20and%20research%20at%20an%20advanced%20level.%20Permission%20was%20given%20and%20the%20grant%20received%20was%20used%20to%20construct%20the%20CHS%20library%20building.%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20the%20CHS%20faculty%20in%20fact%20gave%20up%20its%20own%20promotion%20avenues%20by%20choosing%20to%20build%20the%20library%20rather%20then%20receive%20more%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsix-tables-that-tell-the-story-of-academic-unfreedom-in-india%5C%22%3ESix%20Tables%20that%20Tell%20the%20Story%20of%20Academic%20Unfreedom%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CHS%20faculty%20brought%20resources%20from%20archives%20and%20libraries%20across%20India%20and%20the%20world%20(from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20French%20Archives)%20to%20the%20library%20to%20facilitate%20teaching%20and%20%C2%A0research.%20A%20rich%20collection%20of%20primary%20sources%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20volumes%20of%20inscriptions%2C%20literary%20texts%2C%20and%20archival%20documents%2C%20as%20well%20as%20important%20secondary%20sources%20of%20a%20high%20academic%20standing%20were%20housed%20in%20the%20library.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0The%20library%20was%20able%20to%20bid%20for%20and%20get%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%20the%20rich%20personal%20collection%20of%20the%20eminent%20scholar%20Bernard%20Cohn.%20Collections%20of%20other%20eminent%20scholars%20like%20Satish%20Chandra%20and%20D.N.%20Gupta%20were%20also%20housed%20in%20this%20library.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CHS%20library%20now%20houses%20a%20repository%20that%20was%20carefully%20built%20by%20the%20faculty%20over%20decades%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20research%20and%20teaching%20needs%20of%20the%20Centre.%20The%20library%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20of%20immense%20value%20for%20students%20at%20the%20post-graduate%20and%20research%20levels.%20An%20intensive%20tutorial%20based%20and%20research%20based%20teaching%20programme%20that%20the%20CHS%20conducts%20would%20have%20been%20virtually%20impossible%20without%20such%20a%20departmental%20library%20available%20to%20the%20students.%C2%A0%20In%20fact%2C%20following%20the%20CHS%20example%20other%20centres%20have%20also%20set%20up%20departmental%20libraries%20in%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20was%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20library%20resources%20and%20heavy%20demand%20for%20its%20usage%20that%20the%20need%20was%20felt%20to%20expand%20the%20library.%20After%20the%20CHS%20was%20deemed%20a%20Centre%20for%20Advanced%20Study%20by%20the%20UGC%20another%20grant%20was%20sought%20and%20received%20which%20enabled%20a%20near%20doubling%20of%20the%20space%20in%20the%20CHS%20library%20by%20adding%20a%20floor%20and%20extending%20the%20existing%20CHS%20library%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20history%20of%20the%20CHS%20library%2C%20as%20faculty%20who%20have%20nurtured%20this%20institution%20over%20past%20several%20decades%2C%20we%20feel%20that%20the%20library%E2%80%99s%20relocation%20and%20dispersal%20would%20essentially%20destroy%20this%20fine%20institution%20which%20was%20funded%20specifically%20for%20the%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20therefore%20sincerely%20urge%20the%20University%20to%20reverse%20this%20hasty%20decision%20which%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20taken%20without%20even%20consulting%20the%20CHS%20faculty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfs.%20Romila%20Thapar%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnHarbans%20Mukhia%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnJ.N.%20Panikkar%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnSuvira%20Jaiswal%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnMridula%20Mukherjee%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnDilbagh%20Singh%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnAditya%20Mukherjee%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnNeeladri%20Bhattacharya%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnYogesh%20Sharma%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnArvind%20Sinha%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnKumku