20of%20state.%20The%20BJP%20National%20Executive%20decided%20to%20give%20statehood%20to%20Delhi.%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20promising%20people%20that%20they%20would%20make%20Delhi%20a%20state...%20It%20was%20part%20of%20the%20party%20manifesto%20since%201989%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chadha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20tell%20Amit%20Shah%20ji%2C%20don't%20be%20Nehruvadi%2C%20be%20Advaniwadi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20AAP%20leader%20also%20accused%20the%20party%20of%20insulting%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20crisis%20came%20that%20you%20had%20to%20go%20against%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%3F%20This%20is%20an%20insult%20of%20the%20country's%20top%20court.%20The%20BJP%20given%20a%20message%20that%20it%20doesn't%20care%20what%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20says%2C%20they%20have%20challenged%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20executive%20order%20that%20was%20passed%20barely%20a%20week%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20decision%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20AAP%20government.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ordinance%20and%20the%20proposed%20law%20to%20replace%20it%20over-rides%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20that%20ceded%20Delhi's%20administrative%20control%20to%20the%20elected%20government.%20After%20an%20eight-year%20tussle%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20ruled%20that%20the%20elected%20government%20is%20the%20boss%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ordinance%20created%20a%20National%20Capital%20Civil%20Services%20Authority%20which%20is%20tasked%20with%20postings%20and%20transfers%20of%20bureaucrats%20serving%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20the%20Principal%20Home%20Secretary%20are%20members%20who%20can%20vote%20on%20issues.%20The%20final%20arbiter%20is%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691413200000%