and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI'd%20describe%20myself%20as%20the%20godmother%20of%20the%20internet.%20I%20wrote%20around%20136%20poems%20for%20Beanie%20Babies%20and%20created%20the%20website%20that%20helped%20turn%20them%20into%20a%20pop%20culture%20sensation.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223673%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lina%20Trivedi%20as%20a%20college%20kid%20at%20the%20Ty%20warehouse%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c93d2ccf0778001968b225%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222755%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELina%20Trivedi%20at%20Ty%2C%20Inc.%20with%20stuffed%20animals.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lina%20Trivedi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20parents%20came%20from%20India%20in%201972%2C%20and%20I%20was%20born%20the%20year%20after%20in%201973.%20I%20was%20raised%20with%20very%20typical%20immigrant%20values%3A%20I%20did%20well%20in%20school%2C%20especially%20math.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22835%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lina%20and%20her%20mother%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c93beb048ff200190f1d78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22626%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20young%20Lina%20Trivedi%20and%20her%20mother.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lina%20Trivedi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20parents%20first%20came%20here%2C%20they%20didn't%20speak%20English%20to%20me%2C%20so%20for%20the%20first%20five%20years%20of%20my%20life%2C%20I%20didn't%20speak%20English.%20But%20math%20is%20a%20universal%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20I%20was%207%20years%20old%2C%20my%20parents%20bought%20the%20IBM%205150%2C%20the%20first-ever%20PC.%20My%20mom%20made%20me%20read%20the%20DOS%201.0%20manual%20three%20times.%20Because%20math%20came%20naturally%20to%20me%2C%20computer%20programming%20did%2C%20too.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222831%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lina%20Trivedi%2C%20her%20brother%20and%20her%20father%20at%20the%20Gifted%20Program%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64caa17d95fe1f0019df3816%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222123%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELina%20Trivedi%20learned%20computer%20programming%20when%20she%20was%20in%20the%20second%20grade%20at%20a%20gifted%20program%2C%20pictured%20above.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lina%20Trivedi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20college%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20through%20newspaper%20ads%20for%20a%20part-time%20job%20when%20I%20came%20across%20an%20ad%20for%20Ty%2C%20Inc.%20I%20gave%20them%20a%20call%20and%20basically%20landed%20the%20job%20on%20the%20spot.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221387%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lina%20Trivedi%20in%201994%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c95d25048ff200190f4d18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221040%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELina%20Trivedi%20in%201994.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lina%20Trivedi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20college%20in%20my%20last%20year%20to%20be%20at%20Ty%20full%20time.%20My%20parents%20were%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20you%20doing%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20flak%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%201993%2C%20a%20year%20after%20I%20began%20working%20at%20Ty%2C%20Inc.%2C%20Beanie%20Babies%20were%20born.%20I%20thought%20they%20were%20cute%20and%20addicting%3A%20Once%20you%20pick%20them%20up%2C%20they're%20difficult%20to%20put%20down%20because%20the%20beans%20in%20them%20make%20them%20fun%20to%20play%20with.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221868%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22beanie%20babies%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c93dc3cf0778001968b33f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221401%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETy%20Warner%2C%20founder%20of%20Ty%2C%20Inc.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Barreras%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20early%201995%2C%20I%20approached%20Ty%20Warner%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Ty%2C%20Inc.%2C%20and%20pitched%20the%20idea%20of%20creating%20a%20website%20for%20Beanie%20Babies.%20It%20was%20like%20being%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20the%20perfect%20storm.%20The%20impact%20of%20Beanie%20Babies%20without%20the%20internet%20just%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20the%20same.%20We%20had%20people%20going%20out%20to%20get%20computers%20just%20to%20access%20the%20Ty%20website.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22829%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20of%20Ty%20website%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c93c8ccf0778001968b08d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22622%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screenshot%20of%20the%20early%20Beanie%20Babies%20website.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lina%20Trivedi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recruited%20my%20brother%20to%20Ty%20to%20help%20with%20building%20out%20a%20massive%20catalog%20for%20Beanie%20Babies%3A%20I%20had%20to%20cut%20these%20pictures%20of%20each%20toy%20that%20the%20photographer%20had%20taken%2C%20then%20upload%20them%20onto%20Photoshop%2C%20and%20then%20add%20them%20to%20the%20catalog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20brother%20and%20I%20built%20the%20first%20draft%20of%20the%20site%20together%20in%20about%20a%20week%20or%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20website%20was%20a%20way%20of%20connecting%20with%20customers.%20We%20tapped%20into%20the%20people.%20I%20think%20I%20was%20the%20only%20person%20in%20the%20entire%20company%20that%20had%20a%20pulse%20on%20what%20people%20on%20the%20outside%20really%20wanted.%20All%20the%20physical%20mail%20%E2%80%94%20artwork%2C%20letters%2C%20cards%20%E2%80%94%20and%20emails%20were%20read%20by%20me%20and%20my%20brother.%20We%20soaked%20in%20information%20from%20collectors%20and%20customers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lina%20Trivedi's%20desk%20at%20Ty%20Inc.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.