cated%20the%20house%20days%20after%20he%20was%20stripped%20of%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20membership%20on%20March%2024%20after%20he%20got%20a%20two-year%20jail%20term%20in%20the%20Modi%20surname%20case.%20A%20punishment%20of%20two%20years%20and%20above%20automatically%20disqualifies%20a%20lawmaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20living%20at%20his%20mother%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%2010%20Janpath%20Road%20residence%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Senior%20Congress%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhary%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20house%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20housing%20committee.%20He%20wanted%20to%20apply%20on%20behalf%20of%20Mr%20Gandhi%20but%20he%20was%20told%20that%20under%20the%20rules%2C%20only%20Mr%20Gandhi%20can%20apply%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20accused%20the%20Centre%20of%20political%20vendetta%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Housing%20Committee%20asked%20Mr%20Gandhi%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20government%20accommodation.%20It%20started%20with%20an%20impromptu%20%26quot%3BMera%20ghar%20aapka%20ghar%20(my%20home%20is%20your%20home)%26quot%3B%20campaign%20across%20the%20country%20and%20Mr%20Gandhi%20was%20swamped%20with%20offers%20to%20stay%20with%20various%20Congress%20leaders%20and%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Congress%20leader%20Ajay%20Rai%20was%20the%20first%20to%20symbolically%20dedicate%20his%20home%20to%20Mr%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20dictators%20of%20the%20country%20want%20to%20snatch%20the%20residence%20of%20our%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20But%20they%20do%20not%20know%20that%20the%20houses%20of%20crores%20of%20party%20workers%20across%20the%20country%20belong%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20was%20reinstated%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20put%20his%20conviction%20on%20hold%20on%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BNo%20reason%20has%20been%20given%20by%20the%20trial%20judge%20for%20imposing%20maximum%20sentence%2C%20the%20order%20of%20conviction%20needs%20to%20be%20stayed%20pending%20final%20adjudication%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judges%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Gujarat%20court%20had%20handed%20Mr%20Gandhi%20a%20two-year%20jail%20term%20over%20his%20comments%20on%20PM%20Modi's%20surname.%20At%20a%20rally%20in%20Karnataka's%20Kolar%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20general%20election%2C%20in%20a%20dig%20at%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20come%20all%20the%20thieves%20have%20Modi%20as%20the%20common%20surname%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20was%20accused%20of%20insulting%20a%20backward%20community%20and%20a%20police%20case%20was%20filed%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691410200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fvgpani68_rahul-gandhi-pti-_625x300_07_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-rahul-gandhi-get-his-government-house-back-rules-say-4276828%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20reinstated%20in%20parliament%2C%20will%20need%20to%20re-apply%20to%20the%20parliamentary%20housing%20committee%20to%20get%20his%20Tughlaq%20Lane%20home%20back.%20The%20house%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20allotted%20to%20anyone.%20Sources%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20would%20be%20re-allotted%20the%20house%20again%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-rahul-gandhi-get-his-government-house-back-rules-say-4276828%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-rahul-gandhi-get-his-government-house-back-rules-say-4276828%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-rahul-gandhi-get-his-government-house-back-rules-say-4276828%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maruti%20Suzuki%20is%20now%20the%201st%20and%202n