ey%20has%20been%20given%20to%20Naxalites%20and%20to%20journalists%20like%20Rohini%20Singh%20and%20Swati%20Chaturvedi%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccreate%20an%20atmosphere%20against%20India%E2%80%9D%20for%20which%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20have%20been%20given%20Chinese%20money%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20Congress%20received%20money%20from%20China%20between%202005%20and%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBetween%202005%20and%202014%2C%20whenever%20there%20was%20a%20crisis%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20received%20money%20from%20China.%20In%202008%2C%20they%20invited%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20In%202017%2C%20they%20were%20talking%20to%20the%20Chinese%20during%20the%20Doklam%20crisis%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20took%20the%20names%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20and%20Randeep%20Surjewala%20and%20said%20they%20are%20associated%20with%20the%20Chinese.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(Congress)%20want%20to%20break%20India%20by%20using%20Chinese%20social%20media%20and%20journalists%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20links%20with%20the%20Chinese%20need%20to%20be%20probed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20about%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F05%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fneville-roy-singham-china-propaganda.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20article%20claims%20that%20an%20American%20millionaire%2C%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%2C%20works%20closely%20with%20the%20Chinese%20government%20media%20machine%20to%20finance%20its%20propaganda%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20a%20think%20tank%20in%20Massachusetts%20to%20an%20event%20space%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20from%20a%20political%20party%20in%20South%20Africa%20to%20news%20organisations%20in%20India%20and%20Brazil%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20tracked%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20to%20groups%20linked%20to%20Mr.%20Singham%20that%20mix%20progressive%20advocacy%20with%20Chinese%20government%20talking%20points%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20article%20said%20that%20corporate%20filings%20show%20that%20Singham%E2%80%99s%20network%20%E2%80%9Cfinanced%20a%20news%20site%2C%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20sprinkled%20its%20coverage%20with%20Chinese%20government%20talking%20points.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20refers%20to%20a%20video%20titled%20%E2%80%9CChina%E2%80%99s%20history%20continues%20to%20inspire%20the%20working%20classes%E2%80%9D%20on%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20Purkayastha%20for%20a%20statement.%20This%20report%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20and%20when%20a%20response%20is%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENames%20expunged%20from%20records%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaturvedi%20and%20Singh%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20instead%20of%20making%20claims%20inside%20parliament%20using%20his%20parliamentary%20privileges%2C%20Dubey%20should%20try%20making%20these%20claims%20outside%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20parliamentarian%2C%20he%20should%20not%20be%20lying%20in%20parliament%20by%20using%20names%20who%20have%20never%20worked%20with%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20reason%20he%20is%20doing%20this%20is%20because%20we%20have%20always%20countered%20him.%20I%20would%20urge%20him%20to%20repeat%20what%20he%20said%20inside%20the%20House%20outside%20parliament%20because%20there%20can%20be%20legal%20repercussions%20to%20whatever%20you%20say%20and%20there%20is%20no%20parliamentary%20privilege%20outside%20the%20House%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaturvedi%20shared%20a%20record%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20proceedings%20and%20that%20her%20name%20had%20been%20expunged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20record%20also%20showed%20that%20along%20with%20her%2C%20Singh%2C%20Purkayastha%20and%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20names%20had%20also%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDubey%20has%20used%20his%20parliamentary%20privilege%20and%20he%20has%20taken%20my%20name%20in%20the%20House%20but%20I%20challenge%20anyone%20to%20show%20if%20I%20have%20ever%20taken%20even%20a%20penny%20from%3Cem%3E%20NewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20have%20never%20contributed%20to%20them%2C%20never%20written%20for%20them%20and%20never%20even%20appeared%20on%20any%20of%20their%20videos%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Chaturvedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20BJP%20MP%20misusing%20my%20name.%20While%20my%20name%20has%20been%20expunged%2C%20this%20government%20has%20done%20everything%20it%20can%20to%20intimidate%20me%20and%20to%20silence%20me.%20This%20is%20another%20attempt%20to%20silence%20me%20but%20I%20will%20not%20be%20silenced%20and%20I%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20my%20work%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20comments%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20adjourned%20till%202%20pm%20as%20opposition%20MPs%20protested%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAllegations%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20in%20the%20House%2C%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAnand_Journ%2Fstatus%2F1688462947800981504%2Fphoto%2F1%5C%22%3Ewrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Speaker%3C%2Fa%3E%20Om%20Birla%20and%20said%20that%20Dubey%20started%20levelling%20%E2%80%9Clibellous%20and%20defamatory%20charges%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20House%2C%20without%20having%20given%20any%20notice%2C%20let%20alone%20take%20the%20permission%20of%20the%20chair.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20demanded%20that%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20statement%20against%20Gandhi%20be%20expunged%20from%20the%20record%20and%20an%20inquiry%20be%20conducted%20into%20how%20such%20an%20allegation%20was%20permitted%20to%20be%20raised%20on%20the%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%20later%20on%20Monday%2C%20Union%20ministers%20Anurag%20Thakur%20and%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20repeated%20their%20claims%20against%20the%20Congress%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCongress%2C%20China%20and%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20part%20of%20an%20umbilical%20cord.%20In%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Nakli%20Mohabbat%20Ki%20Dukaan%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20Chinese%20goods%20can%20be%20seen%20clearly.%20His%20love%20for%20China%20can%20be%20seen.%20They%20have%20an%20anti-India%20agenda%2C%20and%20%5Bthey%5D%20ran%20a%20break%20India%20campaign%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1688462143904153602%5C%22%3Esaid%20Thakur.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrasekhar%20said%20that%20the%20narratives%20put%20forward%20by%20platforms%20like%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20echoed%20by%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20narratives%20that%20are%20put%20out%20by%20platforms%20like%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20other%20platforms%20that%20are%20operating%20in%20concert%20are%20echoed%20almost%20blandly%20in%20a%20similar%20fashion%20by%20this%20political%20leader%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20goes%20abroad%20and%20says%20exactly%20the%20same%20things%20%E2%80%93%20democracy%20is%20under%20danger%2C%20judiciary%20is%20compromised%2C%20EVMs%20are%20compromised.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20complex%20conspiracy.%20This%20is%20a%20network%20of%20operators%20being%20funded%2C%20being%20fanned%20by%20vested%20interests%20outside%20the%20country%2C%20who%20are%20opposed%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20rise%2C%20opposed%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20presence%20in%20the%20global%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1688467961869451265%5C%22%3Ehe%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20refuted%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20and%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CPM%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%20are%20experts%20in%20one%20thing%20%E2%80%93%20lying.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20posed%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1688488006309543936%5C%22%3E%20ten%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20dared%20the%20government%20to%20answer%20them%2C%20including%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20Chinese%20encroachment%2C%20and%20when%20the%20status%20quo%20of%20April%202020%20will%20be%20restored%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20as%20well%20as%20questions%20on%20how%20far%20China%20entered%20the%20official%20territory%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691409869000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-mp-nishikant-dubey-rahul-gandhi-newsclick-independent-journalists-chinese-links-nyt-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20independent%20journalists%20%E2%80%93%20Rohini%20Singh%20and%20Swati%20Chaturvedi%20%E2%80%93%20have%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20got%20their%20names%20expunged%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20records.%20The%20Congress%20has%20demanded%20expunging%20Gandhi's%20name%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20ancient%20skull%20unlike%20any%20human%20ever%20seen%20is%20baffling%20scientists%20and%20could%20rewrite%20the%20story%20of%20our%20evolution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%203D%20scan%20of%20facial%20remains%20shows%20what%20we%20know%20of%20the%20skull%20uncovered%20in%20East%20Asia.%20This%20skull's%20top%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20modern%20humans%2C%20but%20its%20chin%20is%20more%20like%20an%20archaic%20human.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d0dd0cf5d4870019e2e3f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221096%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20computer-generated%20image%20of%20the%20remains%20from%20the%20skull%20of%20HLD%206%20(shown%20in%20yellow).%3Cp%3EWu%20et%20al.%20PNAS%202019%2C%20doi.org%2F10.1073%2Fpnas.1902396116%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAn%20ancient%20skull%20found%20in%20China%20is%20like%20nothing%20scientists%20have%20ever%20seen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20teen's%20head%20shape%20doesn't%20fit%20with%20any%20of%20the%20early%20human%20relatives%20seen%20to%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20it%20is%20an%20undiscovered%20human%20ancestor%2C%20it%20could%20rewrite%20the%20story%20of%20human%20evolution.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20ancient%20skull%20is%20baffling%20scientists%20because%20it%20looks%20unlike%20any%20known%20human%20ancestor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mystery%20300%2C000-year-old%20skull%20of%20a%20child%20about%2012%20or%2013%20years%20old%20was%20first%20uncovered%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1073%2Fpnas.1902396116%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHualongdong%20in%20East%20China%20in%202019%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20alongside%20a%20leg%20bone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20think%20the%20individual%2C%20known%20only%20as%20HDL%206%2C%20is%20a%20mix%20between%20modern%20humans%20and%20an%20unknown%20hominin%20that%20existed%20in%20China%20at%20that%20time%2C%20Science%20Alert%20reported%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20skull%20has%20facial%20features%20that%20are%20similar%20to%20early%20modern%20humans%2C%20which%20scientists%20think%20began%20to%20branch%20away%20from%20another%20human%20ancestor%20known%20as%20Homo%20erectus%20sometime%20between%20%3Ca%2