0trying%20to%20share%20information%20on%20Ukraine's%20arms%20locations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20security%20service%20said%20it%20foiled%20an%20effort%20to%20assassinate%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20with%20an%20airstrike%2C%20and%20that%20it%20detained%20a%20collaborator%20who%20tried%20to%20reveal%20his%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fssu.gov.ua%2Fnovyny%2Fsbu-zatrymala-rosiisku-informatorku-yaka-hotuvala-povitrianyi-udar-rf-po-mykolaivshchyni-pid-chas-vizytu-prezydenta-ukrainy-video%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20SBU%20said%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Russia%20planned%20to%20use%20information%20gathered%20by%20the%20alleged%20informant%20to%20launch%20a%20massive%20airstrike%20on%20the%20southern%20Mykolaiv%20region%20while%20Zelenskyy%20was%20visiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fbroadcasts%2F1rmGPkodnrQKN%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espokeswoman%20for%20Ukraine's%20armed%20forces%20said%20the%20SBU%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20able%20to%20%26quot%3Bfoil%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20president%20during%20a%20recent%20trip%20to%20Mykolaiv%2C%26quot%3B%20describing%20it%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Baborted%20assassination%20attempt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20tried%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20timings%20and%20route%20for%20Zelenskyy's%20visit%2C%20but%20the%20SBU%20learned%20about%20her%20efforts%20in%20advance%20and%20put%20extra%20security%20in%20place%20during%20his%20trip%2C%20the%20SBU%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BZelenskyy%20is%20safe%2C%20the%20plot%20was%20foiled%20in%20advance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokeswoman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20tracking%20the%20woman%20they%20also%20found%20she%20was%20trying%20to%20locate%20where%20Ukraine's%20electronic%20warfare%20systems%20and%20ammunition%20warehouses%20were%20placed%2C%20the%20SBU%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20published%20screenshots%20of%20text%20messages%20consistent%20with%20an%20exchange%20between%20an%20informant%20and%20handler%20but%20with%20few%20specifics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20was%20arrested%20on%20Monday%20after%20Ukraine%20learned%20the%20extent%20of%20her%20%26quot%3Btreason%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20armed%20forces%20spokeswoman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20now%20faces%20up%20to%2012%20years%20in%20prison%2C%20the%20SBU%20said%2C%20identifying%20her%20as%20a%20resident%20of%20the%20city%20of%20Ochakov%2C%20in%20Mykolaiv%2C%20and%20a%20former%20saleswoman%20in%20a%20military%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20armed%20forces%20spokeswoman%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bturned%20collaborator%20by%20FSB%20agents%20and%20continued%20to%20work%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FSB%20is%20Russia's%20main%20security%20and%20spy%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20when%20the%20attack%20on%20Zelenskyy%20was%20planned.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.president.gov.ua%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fu-den-medichnogo-pracivnika-volodimir-zelenskij-vidvidav-lik-84545%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHe%20was%20last%20recorded%20visiting%20Mykolaiv%20at%20the%20end%20of%20July%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20he%20also%20made%20trips%20there%20earlier%20in%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20Russian%20attempts%20to%20assassinate%20Zelenskyy%20have%20been%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelenskyy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-zelensky-russia-backed-assassination-attempts-report-2022-3%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Esurvived%20at%20least%20three%20assassination%20attempts%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Russia-backed%20agents%20in%20the%20first%20few%20weeks%20of%20the%20invasion%2C%20%3Ca%20data-xid%3D%5C%22fr1691401475073gcb%5C%22%20data-ml-dynamic-type%3D%5C%22sl%5C%22%20data-ml%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20data-skimlinks-tracking%3D%5C%22xid%3Afr1691401475073gcb%5C%22%20data-ml-dynamic%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22b