ns%20Command%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20including%20in%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20move%20that%20generated%20a%20lot%20of%20buzz%2C%20the%20US%20sent%20more%20than%20700%20Switchblades%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20mostly%20the%206-pound%20Switchblade%20300%20but%20also%20a%20few%20of%20the%2033-pound%20Switchblade%20600.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Remain%20of%20a%20Russian-made%20Shahed%20136%20at%20an%20exhibition%20showing%20remains%20of%20missiles%20and%20drones%20that%20Russia%20used%20to%20attack%20Kyiv%20on%20May%2012%2C%202023%20in%20Kyiv%2C%20Ukraine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64843f7005024f0019028f8a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERemains%20of%20a%20Russian-made%20Shahed-136%20used%20to%20attack%20Kyiv%20on%20display%20in%20May.%3Cp%3EOleksii%20Samsonov%20%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECuriously%2C%20the%20Army's%202024%20missile%20procurement%20budget%20doesn't%20include%20any%20Switchblades.%20One%20reason%20may%20be%20their%20price.%20Each%20Switchblade%20costs%20%2458%2C000%2C%20though%20defense%20writer%20David%20Hambling%20estimates%20the%20true%20cost%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.19fortyfive.com%2F2023%2F07%2Fthe-u-s-army-wont-buy-anymore-switchblade-300-kamikaze-drones%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabout%20%2480%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20apiece.%20But%20Ukraine%20is%20launching%20swarms%20of%20militarized%20commercial%20drones%20that%20cost%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20each.%20Even%20if%20some%20are%20shot%20down%20or%20disrupted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-losing-10000-drones-month-russia-electronic-warfare-rusi-report-2023-5%5C%22%3ERussian%20jamming%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20economics%20favor%20the%20cheaper%20drone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20also%20interesting%20about%20LASSO%20is%20that%20the%20Army%20is%20emphasizing%20it%20as%20an%20anti-armor%20weapon.%20%26quot%3BThis%20anti-tank%20capability%20is%20a%20key%20contributor%20to%20our%20efforts%20to%20increase%20the%20lethality%20of%20the%20Army%20of%202030's%20IBCT%20and%20maintain%20overmatch%20against%20our%20near-peer%20threats%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Army%20spokesman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20frequent%20videos%20of%20Ukrainian%20drones%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2JbZEK9kwqQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrashing%20into%20Russian%20tanks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20these%20are%20improvised%20weapons.%20The%20Switchblade%20300's%20warhead%20is%20only%20the%20size%20of%20a%2040%20mm%20grenade%2C%20while%20the%20Switchblade%20600%2C%20which%20is%20designed%20to%20kill%20armored%20vehicles%2C%20is%20expensive.%20It's%20not%20clear%20what%20kind%20of%20warhead%20LASSO%20will%20pack%2C%20and%20the%20Army%20didn't%20mention%20cost%20in%20its%20announcement%2C%20but%20if%20combat%20in%20Ukraine%20is%20a%20guide%2C%20LASSO%20will%20target%20the%20thinner%20armor%20on%20top%20of%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20numerous%20top-attack%20anti-tank%20weapons%20%E2%80%94%20the%20US-made%20Javelin%20missile%20and%20laser-guided%20artillery%20shells%20such%20as%20US's%20Excalibur%20and%20Russia's%20Krasnopol%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few%20%E2%80%94%20but%20these%20munitions%20cost%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20each.%20If%20the%20Army%20can%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20build%20a%20LASSO%20that's%20powerful%20enough%20to%20destroy%20a%20tank%20but%20cheap%20enough%20for%20mass%20employment%2C%20the%20impact%20could%20be%20immense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20a%20master's%20in%20political%20sci