s%20vendetta%20identity%20badge%20is%20of%20a%20graceless%20and%20fuming%20loser%2C%20whose%20approach%20is%20to%20control%2C%20control%20n%20control%20everything%2C%20by%20hook%20or%20crook%20and%20usually%20more%20by%20crook%20than%20by%20hook%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20quoted%20German%20theologian%20Martin%20Niemoller's%20timeless%20lines%2C%20%26quot%3BFirst%20they%20came...%26quot%3B%2C%20to%20warn%20political%20parties%20that%20have%20announced%20support%20to%20the%20centre%20on%20the%20Delhi%20services%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20collectively%20oppose%20this%20cause%20one%20day%20this%20federalism%20knock%20could%20come%20at%20your%20door.%20Sabka%20number%20aayega%20(everyone's%20turn%20will%20come)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20then%20quoted%20quoted%20Niemoller%2C%20%26quot%3BFirst%20they%20came%20for%20the%20socialists%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20speak%20out%20because%20I%20was%20not%20a%20socialist.%20Then%20they%20came%20for%20the%20trade%20unionists%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20speak%20out%20because%20I%20was%20not%20a%20trade%20unionist.%20Then%20they%20came%20for%20the%20Jews%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20speak%20out%20because%20I%20was%20not%20a%20Jew.%20Then%20they%20came%20for%20me%20and%20there%20was%20no%20one%20left%20to%20speak%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lines%2C%20used%20by%20Niemoller%20to%20criticise%20the%20silence%20of%20German%20intellectuals%20and%20religious%20leaders%20during%20the%20rise%20of%20Nazism%2C%20is%20routinely%20used%20to%20hit%20out%20at%20people%20who%20do%20not%20speak%20out%20against%20authoritarian%20regimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691401980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F4r5fiek8_abhishek-singhvi_625x300_07_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-services-bill-delhi-bill-debate-rajya-sab