20part%20of%20the%20news%20website%E2%80%99s%20public%20outreach%20and%20fund-raising%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20evening%20also%20featured%20the%20singer-educator%20Shabnam%20Virmani%20explaining%20and%20performing%20works%20from%20Kabir%20%E2%80%93%20the%20medieval%20Indian%20poet-saint%20whose%20work%20was%20deeply%20imbued%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20fraternity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20questions%20from%20Chishti%20and%20the%20audience%2C%20Prakash%20Raj%20spoke%20about%20the%20meaning%20of%20fraternity%2C%20why%20it%20was%20under%20strain%20in%20India%20today%2C%20the%20all-pervading%20sense%20of%20fear%20that%20seems%20to%20have%20gripped%20so%20many%20and%20the%20effect%20of%20this%20fear%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20film%20industry.%20he%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20work%20he%20is%20doing%2C%20especially%20through%20the%20medium%20of%20theatre%20to%20strengthen%20fraternity%2C%20and%20how%20he%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20fearlessness%20and%20broad-mindedness%20of%20the%20young%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20theme%20of%20the%20evening%2C%20Siddharth%20Varadarajan%2C%20a%20founding%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20said%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98fraternity%E2%80%99%20figures%20prominently%20in%20the%20preamble%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20alongside%20justice%2C%20liberty%20and%20equality%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20it%20is%20a%20word%20we%20often%20forget%20or%20ignore%20even%20though%20its%20spirit%20is%20so%20central%20to%20who%20we%20are%20as%20a%20people.%20Fraternity%20is%20that%20magical%20element%20that%20assures%20each%20and%20every%20one%20of%20us%20of%20our%20dignity%20as%20individuals%20%E2%80%93%20and%2C%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20ensures%20our%20unity%20as%20a%20people%20and%20nation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20quoted%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20words%20to%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20in%201949%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CFraternity%20means%20a%20sense%20of%20common%20brotherhood%20of%20all%20Indians-of%20Indians%20being%20one%20people.%20It%20is%20the%20principle%20which%20gives%20unity%20and%20solidarity%20to%20social%20life%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20and%20said%20what%20this%20means%20is%20that%20%E2%80%9Cif%20you%20attack%20the%20dignity%20of%20an%20individual%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20their%20ethnicity%20or%20language%2C%20religion%20or%20caste%2C%20sexuality%20or%20food%20habits%20or%20beliefs%20%E2%80%93%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ethen%20you%20attack%20the%20very%20foundations%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07111456%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-07-at-11.00.11-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07111456%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-07-at-11.00.11-AM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07111456%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-07-at-11.00.11-AM-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07111456%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-07-at-11.00.11-AM-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-666938%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESiddharth%20Varadarajan%20at%20The%20Wire%20Dialogues.%20Photo%3A%20Devi%20Dutt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThink%20about%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Varadarajan%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhen%20you%20reflect%20upon%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Manipur%20or%20Haryana%20or%20Kashmir%20today.%20Think%20about%20this%20when%20you%20read%20about%20train%20passengers%20being%20shot%20dead%20because%20of%20the%20beard%20they%20had%20or%20the%20clothes%20they%20wore.%20Thin