from%20the%20case%20within%20seven%20days.%20Otherwise%20they%20have%20threatened%20a%20%3Cem%3Echakka-jam%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESube%20Singh%20Bohra%2C%20former%20sarpanch%20of%20Wazirabad%20in%20Sector%2057%2C%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20see%20the%20evidence%20against%20the%20men%20that%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20the%20violence.%20The%20families%20are%20being%20harassed%20and%20targeted%20by%20those%20living%20near%20the%20mosque%2C%20but%20we%20will%20not%20let%20this%20happen%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20hundreds%20of%20Muslim%20men%20working%20in%20Gurugram%20as%20carpenters%2C%20barbers%2C%20vegetable%20vendors%2C%20mechanics%2C%20and%20cab%20drivers%2C%20and%20we%20have%20always%20supported%20them%2C%20but%20now%20we%20will%20ensure%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20any%20support%20from%20anywhere%20as%20they%20are%20responsible%20for%20disrupting%20peace%20in%20the%20city.%20Muslims%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20love%20or%20work%20in%20the%20city.%20We%20appeal%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20city%20not%20to%20rent%20out%20apartments%20or%20slums%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kulbhushan%20Bhardwaj%2C%20a%20Bajrang%20Dal%20member%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDLF%20Gurugram%20senior%20police%20officer%20Vikas%20Kaushik%20told%20ANI%20that%20the%20organisers%20had%20told%20the%20police%20the%20event%20would%20be%20peaceful.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20past%20two-three%20days%2C%20Gurugram%20has%20been%20peaceful.%20No%20incident%20has%20been%20reported.%20We%20feel%20that%20today%E2%80%99s%20panchayat%20will%20be%20carried%20out%20peacefully.%20We%20have%20had%20talks%20with%20all%20sides.%20They%20have%20assured%20us%20that%20the%20panchayat%20will%20happen%20peacefully%E2%80%A6%20The%20panchayat%20starts%20at%209%20am.%20Some%20500-1%2C000%20people%20are%20expected%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kaushik%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20did%20not%20say%20why%20police%20was%20not%20intervening%20despite%20prohibitory%20orders%20being%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20flagged%20this%20boycott%20call%20on%20Sunday%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20letter%20that%20made%20the%20same%20demand%20written%20by%20a%20panchayat%20sarpanch%20on%20his%20official%20letterhead.%20A%20four-member%20delegation%20from%20the%20party%20also%20visited%20affected%20areas%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20letter%20on%20the%20letterhead%20of%20the%20Jainabad%20Panchayat%20Sarpanch%20Bhavna%20Yadav%2C%20from%20Block%20Dahina%2C%20District%20Rewari%2C%20Haryana%2C%20exposes%20the%20bitter%20reality%20of%20organised%20discrimination%20against%20minorities%20which%20is%20being%20bred%20systematically%20under%20the%20BJP%20rule%2C%E2%80%9D%20CPI%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fcommunal-violence-communist-party-of-india-delegation-in-haryana-flags-muslim-boycott-call%2Fcid%2F1957186%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20content%20of%20the%20letter%20is%20shocking.%20It%20submits%20to%20the%20local%20police%20authorities%20a%20decision%20to%20not%20allow%20Muslims%20or%20miscreants%20to%20do%20any%20business%20or%20hawker%20activity%20in%20the%20panchayat%20area.%20It%20also%20equalises%20Muslims%20to%20burglars%20and%20cattle-thieves%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20letter%20says%20that%20these%20steps%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20ensure%20peace%20in%20the%20village%2C%20automatically%20making%20Muslim%20presence%20the%20sole%20reason%20for%20communal%20disturbance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691382654000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02105433%2F4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindu-mahapanchayat-held-without-permission-in-gurugram-calls-for-boycott-of-muslims%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Those%20attending%20the%20meeting%20also%20alleged%20that%20people%20who%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20attacking%20the%20mosque%20in%20Gurugram%20are%20%26quot%3Binnocent%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindu-mahapanchayat-held-without-permission-in-gurugram-calls-for-boycott-of-muslims%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20Kuki%20People's%20Alliance%20Withdraws%20Support%20From%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20Government%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20124144%2FF1SovOrXoAA5F5U.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Kuki%20People%E2%80%99s%20Alliance%20(KPA)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20party%20with%20two%20sitting%20MLAs%20in%20the%20Manipur%20government%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20%E2%80%93%20on%20Sunday%20announced%20that%20it%20is%20withdrawing%20support%20from%20the%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20careful%20consideration%20of%20the%20current%20conflagration%2C%20the%20continued%20support%20for%20the%20incumbent%20government%20of%20Manipur%2C%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20is%20no%20longer%20fructuous.%20Accordingly%2C%20the%20support%20of%20the%20KPA%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20Manipur%20is%20hereby%20withdrawn%20and%20can%20be%20considered%20null%20and%20void%2C%E2%80%9D%20KPA%20president%20Tongmang%20Haokip%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Sunday%20evening%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fnda-kuki-peoples-alliance-withdraws-support-biren-singh-govt-manipur-8879727%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20KPA%20MLAs%20currently%20in%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20are%20Kimneo%20Hangshing%20and%20Chinlunthang%2C%20representing%20the%20Saikul%20and%20Singat%20constituencies%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20KPA%20is%20a%20new%20party%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20formed%20in%202022%20and%20contested%20its%20first%20elections%20in%20the%20same%20year.%20Members%20of%20the%20party%20had%20attended%20the%20NDA%20meet%20held%20in%20Delhi%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20eight%20other%20Kuki%20MLAs%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20all%20from%20the%20BJP.%20While%20they%20have%20openly%20criticised%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%20his%20handling%20of%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20conflict%2C%20they%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20government.%20All%2010%20Kuki%20MLAs%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-kuki-zomi-mlas-separate-administration%5C%22%3Eearlier%20urged%20the%20Union%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20separate%20administration%20under%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20and%20let%20people%20from%20their%20community%20%E2%80%9Clive%20peacefully%20as%20neighbours%20with%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20assembly%20is%20supposed%20to%20convene%20on%20August%2021.%20The%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Churachandpur%2C%20L.M.%20Khaute%2C%20has%20already%20said%20he%20will%20be%20unable%20to%20attend%20the%20session%20%E2%80%9Cin%20view%20of%20the%20prevailing%20law%20and%20order%20situation%E2%80%9D%2C%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20three%20months%20have%20passed%20since%20ethnic%20conflict%20erupted%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203%2C%20and%20the%20violence%20is%20showing%20no%20signs%20of%20abating.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20six%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20fresh%20rounds%20of%20violence%20%E2%80%93%20leading%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fimphal%2Fmore-central-forces-sent-to-manipur-amid-meitei-outfits-appeal-to-boycott-biren-govt%2Farticleshow%2F102480622.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Esend%20800%20additional%20central%20security%20personnel%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kuki%20groups%20have%20consistently%20held%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20responsible%20for%20failing%20to%20protect%20their%20people%20and%20even%20encouraging%20the%20violence%2C%20Meitei%20groups%20too%20have%20openly%20expressed%20their%20unhappiness%20with%20the%20chief%20minister.%20The%20Coordinating%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Integrity%20(COCOMI)%2C%20an%20umbrella%20organisation%20of%20Meitei%20groups%20which%20has%20been%20supporting%20the%20Singh%20government%20so%20far%20and%20even%20urged%20the%20chief%20minister%20not%20to%20resign%20earlier%2C%20has%20now%20issued%20an%20%E2%80%9Cindefinite%20social%20boycott%E2%80%9D%20appeal%20against%20the%20same%20government%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fimphal%2Fmore-central-forces-sent-to-manipur-amid-meitei-outfits-appeal-to-boycott-biren-govt%2Farticleshow%2F102480622.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resurgence%20in%20violence%2C%20COCOMI%20said%2C%20is%20because%20the%20state%20government%20has%20not%20been%20taking%20heed%20of%20civil%20society%20groups%E2%80%99%20demand%20to%20act%20against%20%E2%80%9CChin%20Kuki%20narco%20terrorists%E2%80%9D.%20The%20group%20also%20criticised%20the%20government%20for%20failing%20to%20convene%20a%20special%20assembly%20session%20on%20the%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691379920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20124144%2FF1SovOrXoAA5F5U.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-kuki-peoples-alliance-withdraws-support-from-n-biren-singh-government%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20KPA%2C%20for