Abb.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ERenowned%20singer%2C%20activist%20and%20writer%20Gaddar%20%E2%80%93%20born%20Gummadi%20Vittal%20Rao%20%E2%80%93%20passed%20away%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Sunday.%20He%20was%2074.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApollo%20Spectra%20Hospital%2C%20Ameerpet%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20he%20passed%20away%20at%203%20pm%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20lung%20and%20urinary%20problems%20and%20advanced%20age%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20suffering%20from%20severe%20heart%20disease%20and%20got%20admitted%20on%20July%2020%2C%202023.%20He%20underwent%20a%20bypass%20surgery%20on%20August%203%2C%202023%20and%20recovered%20from%20it.%20However%2C%20he%20is%20a%20past%20patient%20of%20lung%20and%20urinary%20problems%2C%20which%20along%20with%20advanced%20age%20aggravated%20and%20led%20to%20his%20passing%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20hospital%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Frevolutionary-singer-activist-gaddar-passes-away-hyderabad-180703%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gaddar%20and%20his%20music%20were%20a%20crucial%20part%20of%20the%20Maoist%20movement%20in%20Telangana%20as%20well%20as%20the%20separate%20statehood%20agitation%20since%20the%20late%201960s.%20His%20songs%20highlighted%20state%20exploitation%20and%20marginalisation%20of%20oppressed%20communities%2C%20including%20several%20songs%20on%20extrajudicial%20killings%20and%20police%20torture.%20He%20also%20played%20an%20important%20role%20during%20the%20demand%20for%20statehood%20for%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWatch%20%7C%20How%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGaddar%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Gaddar%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20a%20household%20name%20in%20the%20state%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22ht