%20(UNFCCC).%20The%20UNFCCC%20came%20into%20force%20on%2021%20March%201994%20with%20the%20aim%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324699%2Fawais-ahmed-founded-space-startup-pixxel-hyperspectral-satellite-launch-hyperloop-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20prevent%20%E2%80%9Cdangerous%E2%80%9D%20human%20interference%20with%20the%20climate%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20COP%20meets%20every%20year%20to%20assess%20the%20progress%20that%20has%20been%20made%20towards%20this.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20meetings%20have%20resulted%20in%20several%20legally%20binding%20international%20agreements%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20including%20the%202015%20Paris%20Agreement%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20limit%20global%20warming%20to%20well%20below%202%20degrees%20Celsius%20above%20pre-industrial%20levels%20and%20pursue%20efforts%20to%20limit%20the%20temperature%20increase%20to%201.5%20degrees%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECOP28%20UAE%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2028th%20COP%20is%20being%20hosted%20by%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20at%20Expo%20City%20Dubai%20between%2030%20November%20and%2012%20December%202023.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20COP%20of%20unity%2C%20solidarity%2C%20and%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECOP28%20will%20see%20the%20first%20Global%20Stocktake%20(GST)%2C%20a%20process%20mandated%20by%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20to%20evaluate%20advancements%20towards%20its%20objectives.%20It%20is%20against%20this%20backdrop%20that%20COP28%20will%20bring%20everyone%20to%20the%20table%20to%20recalibrate%2C%20raise%20ambitions%20and%20maximise%20the%20opportunities%20of%20the%20clean%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20of%20this%20year%2C%20the%20UAE%20hosted%20the%20annual%20Abu%20Dhabi%20Sustainability%20Week%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286865%2Feasy-steps-to-be-sustainable-at-home-no-plastic-use-save-money-sustainability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E%20event%20established%20in%202008%20to%20accelerate%20sustainable%20economic%20development%20and%20facilitate%20partnerships%20to%20enable%20the%20energy%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20XX%20edition%20of%20ADSW%20drove%20momentum%20between%20COP27%20and%20COP28%2C%20enabling%20impactful%20and%20continuous%20dialogue%20between%20key%20stakeholders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%20was%20the%20first%20country%20in%20the%20region%20to%20announce%20its%20commitment%20to%20Net%20Zero%20and%20has%20a%20proud%20track%20record%20of%20investing%20in%20the%20energy%20transition.%20This%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F271708%2Fstartup-innovation-convert-renewable-energy-water-uravu-labs-bengaluru-engineer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenewable%20energy%3C%2Fa%3E%20powerhouse%2C%20Masdar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20Climate%20Leadership%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMasdar%20was%20established%20in%202006%20as%20part%20of%20the%20UAE%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20vision%20to%20diversify%20its%20economy%20and%20bring%20about%20a%20cycle%20of%20growth%20and%20innovation.%20His%20Excellency%20Dr%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber%2C%20the%20COP%20President%20Designate%2C%20is%20Masdar%E2%80%99s%20founding%20CEO%20and%20current%20Chairman.%20Under%20his%20leadership%2C%20the%20company%20has%20grown%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20investors%20in%20renewable%20energy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Masdar%20has%20a%20combined%20investment%20portfolio%20valued%20at%20%2430bn.%20It%20is%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20climate%20innovation%2C%20operating%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F287058%2Frenewable-energy-map-india-wind-power-plants-project-largest-solar-park-environment-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecutting-edge%20renewable%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20improving%20lives%20in%20over%2040%20countries%20across%206%20continents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EH.E.%20Dr%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber%20brings%20over%2020%20years%20of%20industry%20knowledge%20and%20experience%20to%20the%20role%20of%20COP%20President-Designate%20and%20is%20uniquely%20positioned%20to%20drive%20critical%20negotiations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20of%20the%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20preeminent%20climate%20champions%2C%20Dr%20Sultan%20has%20outlined%20his%20plans%20to%20deliver%20a%20COP%20for%20all%2C%20underpinned%20by%20the%20belief%20that%20everyone%20must%20be%20on%20board%20in%20order%20to%20accelerate%20progress.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2013%20days%2080%2C000%20participants%2C%20including%20140%20heads%20of%20state%20and%20government%20will%20meet%20in%20the%20UAE%20to%20reduce%20emissions%2C%20protect%20biodiversity%2C%20and%20support%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288116%2Fwhat-antarcticas-40c-weather-iceberg-graveyard-taught-me-about-climate-change%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaffected%20by%20climate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20we%20aren%E2%80%99t%20moving%20fast%20enough%2C%20but%20we%20also%20know%20that%20we%20have%20the%20power%20to%20achieve%20a%20more%20sustainable%20and%20prosperous%20future%2C%20if%20we%20act%20in%20solidarity.%20COP-28%20will%20be%20remembered%20for%20uniting%20everyone%20in%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20drafted%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Masdar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%