%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fdesert-5_11zon-1690808865.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325795%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%2024%20years%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20Colonel%20Mahendra%20Mohan%20Prakash%20Singh%20started%20Oasis%20India%20Camp%20to%20help%20tourists%20from%20across%20the%20world%20experience%20the%20magic%20of%20Jaisalmer%E2%80%99s%20desert%2C%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20both%20luxurious%20and%20replete%20with%20adventure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325795%2Fretired-army-officer-colonel-mahendra-mohan-oasis-luxury-camps-in-jaisalmer%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Portable%20Innovation%20Saves%20Lives%20by%20Bringing%20Doctors%20to%2030%20Lakh%20Pregnant%20Women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAntenatal%20care%20is%20designed%20to%20make%20pregnancy%20safer%20for%20women%20by%20detecting%20complications%20early%20and%20ensuring%20timely%20treatment.%20At%20least%20four%20antenatal%20care%20visits%20are%20recommended%20to%20monitor%20the%20health%20of%20the%20pregnant%20woman%20and%20her%20fetus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20rural%20areas%2C%20about%2054%20percent%20of%20mothers%20attend%20the%20recommended%20visits%2C%20compared%20to%2068.1%20percent%20in%20urban%20areas.%20This%20implies%20that%20roughly%20half%20of%20pregnant%20women%20in%20rural%20regions%20do%20not%20visit%20hospitals%20for%20advised%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20these%20complications%20significantly%20impact%20women%E2%80%99s%20lives.%20In%20India%2C%20there%20were%2097%20maternal%20deaths%20per%201%2C00%2C000%20live%20births%20reported%20between%202018%E2%80%9320.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20behind%20such%20deaths%20is%20that%20women%20avoid%20going%20to%20far-off%20healthcare%20centres%20for%20routine%20checkups.%20The%20complications%2C%20if%20any%2C%20remain%20ignored%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tamil%20Nadu-based%20Senthil%20Kumar%20Murugesan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHigh-risk%20mothers%20are%20usually%20identified%20in%20the%20third%20trimester%2C%20which%20is%20around%20the%20eighth%20month%20of%20pregnancy.%20However%2C%20by%20this%20time%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20often%20too%20late%20to%20effectively%20manage%20complications%20before%20labour.%20This%20can%20lead%20to%20fatal%20outcomes.%20Currently%2C%20all%20records%20are%20maintained%20on%20paper%2C%20and%20if%20mortality%20occurs%2C%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20death%20remains%20unknown.%20There%20are%20no%20data-based%20analyses%20available%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2033-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20least%20four%20antenatal%20care%20visits%20are%20recommended%20to%20monitor%20the%20health%20of%20the%20pregnant%20woman%20and%20her%20fetus.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-2-1690550162-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325680%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20least%20four%20antenatal%20care%20visits%20are%20recommended%20to%20monitor%20the%20health%20of%20the%20pregnant%20woman%20and%20her%20fetus.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20electronics%20and%20communications%20engineer%20by%20profession%2C%20Senthil%20worked%20with%20companies%20like%20Samsung%20and%20Qualcomm%20for%20seven%20years.%20But%20to%20address%20this%20gap%2C%20in%202019%2C%20he%20started%20JioVio%20Healthcare%2C%20an%20IoT-based%20maternal%20healthcare%20startup%20that%20provides%20early%20risk%20monitoring%20services%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20developed%20an%20AI%20tool%20that%20can%20predict%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F141847%2Fhigh-risk-pregnancies-get-help-with-caremother-app%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-risk%20pregnancies%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20second%20trimester.%20This%20helps%20the%20women%20get%20early%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20if%20any%20changes%20are%20needed%20in%20nutrition%2C%20sleep%20cycle%2C%20etc.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20convert%20high-risk%20pregnancies%20into%20low-risk%20ones%20by%20ensuring%20the%20timely%20provision%20of%20medication%20and%20proper%20nutrition%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20informs%20that%20since%202019%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20catered%20to%20more%20than%2030%20lakh%20mothers%20from%2014%2C328%20villages%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Kerala.%20Through%20a%201%2C000-day%20care%20programme%2C%20he%20has%20also%20helped%20at%20least%207%2C320%20high-risk%20pregnant%20women%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20sister%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20to%20lifesaving%20innovation%20for%20rural%20women%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20first%20came%20across%20the%20pregnancy%20healthcare%20gap%20when%20his%20sister%20was%20pregnant%20in%202016.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20a%20career-driven%20woman%20and%20would%20miss%20her%20antenatal%20appointments%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20time.%20Also%2C%20the%20distance%20from%20her%20village%20to%20the%20hospital%20is%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20Madurai%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-3-1690550200.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senthil%20informs%20that%20since%202019%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20catered%20to%20more%20than%20three%20lakh%20mothers%20from%2014%2C328%20villages%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Kerala.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-3-1690550200.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-3-1690550200-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-3-1690550200-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-3-1690550200-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-3-1690550200-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325681%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESenthil%20informs%20that%20since%202019%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20catered%20to%20more%20than%2030%20lakh%20mothers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20concern%20for%20her%20drove%20him%20to%20develop%20a%20prototype%20of%20a%20device%20that%20could%20monitor%20one%E2%80%99s%20vitals%20like%20blood%20glucose%20and%20blood%20pressure.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20my%20sister%20does%20not%20go%20into%20the%20labour%20room%20with%20any%20complications%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20experience%20made%20me%20realise%20that%20women%20face%20significant%20challenges%20when%20visiting%20hospitals%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F72679%2Fcare-nx-doorstep-diagnosis-innovative-technology-pregnancy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantenatal%20care%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20long%20travel%20times%20and%20waiting%20periods%20of%20five%20to%20six%20hours%20for%20a%20short%20consultation%20lead%20many%20women%20to%20avoid%20these%20visits%20and%20postpone%20them%20to%20the%20next%20month.%20However%2C%20this%20delay%20prevents%20potential%20risks%20from%20being%20assessed%20in%20a%20timely%20manner.%20I%20became%20aware%20of%20the%20alarming%20mortality%20rates%20among%20tribal%20and%20rural%20pregnant%20women%20and%20felt%20determined%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20after%20creating%20a%20simple%20device%20for%20his%20sister%2C%20Senthil%20felt%20inspired%20to%20assist%20more%20women%2C%20particularly%20those%20in%20rural%20and%20remote%20areas.%20His%20aim%20was%20to%20help%20them%20monitor%20essential%20vitals%20usually%20recorded%20during%20antenatal%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20years%20of%20clinical%20trials%2C%20he%20founded%20JioVio%20Healthcare%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMonitoring%20vitals%20in%20a%20single%20device%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20process%20of%20reaching%20out%20to%20rural%20women%2C%20Senthil%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20with%20the%20state%20governments.%20After%20contacting%20them%2C%20the%20secretaries%20inform%20us%20about%20the%20districts%20with%20high%20maternal%20mortality.%20We%20then%20approach%20the%20district%20collector%2C%20who%20onboards%20block-level%20officers%2C%20healthcare%20workers%2C%20and%20rural%20women.%20When%20any%20of%20the%20rural%20women%20get%20pregnant%2C%20a%20mobile%20application%20is%20used%20to%20track%20their%20health%20and%20conduct%20monthly%20checkups.%E2%80%9D